GOOGLE CLOUD OCR SETUP AND INTEGRATION


INSTALLATION OF API
brew install --cask google-cloud-sdk   

POST COMMAND
POST https://vision.googleapis.com/v1/images:annotate

COMMAND for enabling vision cloud
gcloud services enable vision.googleapis.com --project project-5b9d9537-1e48-4b04-b26                             

COMMAND for AUTH login
gcloud auth application-default login

COMMAND for AUTH SETUP 
gcloud auth application-default set-quota-project project-5b9d9537-1e48-4b04-b26

COMMAND for gcloud vision upload
gcloud ml vision detect-text FILENAME --project project-5b9d9537-1e48-4b04-b26


